summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Sixtieth Street from 28th Avenue N.W. to 32nd Avenue N.W. in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 20609, creating Local Improvement District No. 2057 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
